      <title>DVD 过时，电子烟流行，印度尼西亚重塑通胀篮子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/dvds-are-out-vapes-are-in-as-indonesia-recasts-inflation-basket</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚正在彻底改革其通货膨胀篮子，用电子烟和电子烟油等更常见的购买商品取代 DVD 和印刷杂志等商品，以衡量消费者价格趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/dvds-are-out-vapes-are-in-as-indonesia-recasts-inflation-basket</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 07:14:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
